descript.abstract: Every roadway in Dakota County has a street address range assigned to each side of the street. The street address map can be used to map either single or multiple street address locations. The street address database can be used to map the location of an address when typed into the computer, or read a list of addresses from a file and display their many locations.
descript.purpose: The street address database could be used to direct either a transit vehicle or emergency response vehicle to a given address. It could also be used to map the location of clients, public meeting participants, or any address database.

idinfo.accconst: Licensed. Street centerline data is available to anyone. Fees are charged according to the Dakota County GIS Data pricing policy. For current pricing information visit the digital data portion of the Dakota County Office of Geographic Information Systems website at http://www.co.dakota.mn.us/gis/data/digital_data.htm.
